        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The lvl 24 pet spell cannot be purchased from an SK vendor as SKs don't get this spell.  I had the best luck getting Words of Allure in High Keep.  The goblins seem to drop them only rarely though.  I was able to get four copies only and then botched the combine all four times.  If you get lucky and come across the words I would suggest finding someone with a higher research skill to do the combine for you as this spell seems to have a particularly nasty fail rate (though admittedly this could have just been a nasty coincidence for me).  </P><P>I also would not recommed putting a huge amount of time into finding them.  I gave up and just made do with the 20 pet until I hit 29.  It was a little tougher and resulted in a bit more downtime but it beat running all over the world looking for those words and losing hunting time.  The downtime results from the fact that you have to burn more mana to compensate for your pets decreasing ability to deal damage to experience giving mobs as you approach 29.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
