         Allure also drops off shadowed men in Lavastorm. I'm pretty sure it also drops in Stonebrunt - the critters in that zone are exceptionally well-read.</P><P>Detachment also drops, rarely, in the Knight Room in Unrest. The problem is that you will get aggro from the barroom. So, get a couple of druids in wolf form and have them Harmony each room. Then kill everything. This is a fun camp with decent drops and, if things go terribly wrong, the druids can evac the group to the entry tunnel.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
