        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         There is actually a quest for words of detachment and allure, but they may be broken.  They involve drops in MM and Unrest.  The Unrest drops are rare drops, but as far as I can tell, no one has found the MM drops.  These words and several others involve these items that are supposed to drop in MM: charred dagger, charred wood wand, ebon dagger, ebon wand.  I have tried the wand of tears and wand of weeping and the sacrificial dagger as well as the burnt wand that drops in beffallen and the shadow dagger from the ilse goblin chief.  As I can find no reference to anyone completing the words quests involving MM drops, I think its broken.  <BR>I found my words of detachtment at the OT outpost vendors and the centaur vendor in SK.  I have also seen it drop in the basement and 2nd floor of unrest.  I had a bunch of Allure which I dont remember what dropped them.</P><P>Suetekh<BR>Necromancer of 34 Reanimations<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
